### List all documents (default page=1, pageSize=20)
GET http://localhost:3001/documents

### List documents filtered by format
GET http://localhost:3001/documents?formatCode=edifact

### List documents with simple text search
GET http://localhost:3001/documents?search=carrefour

### List documents with pagination
GET http://localhost:3001/documents?page=1&pageSize=2

### Get a single document by code (now includes analyses + messages)
GET http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000001

### Get raw EDIFACT purchase order content
GET http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000001/content

### Get raw XML invoice content
GET http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000002/content

### Get raw JSON despatch advice content
GET http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000003/content

### Get raw CSV catalog content
GET http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000004/content

### Get a presigned download URL (valid 1 hour)
GET http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000001/download-url

### --- Upload a new document (multipart) ---
### Use the file picker in REST Client; or run the curl command below.
### curl -F "file=@./apps/api/src/seed/sample-documents/purchase-order-carrefour.edi" \
###      -F "description=Demo upload" \
###      -F "tags=demo,upload" \
###      http://localhost:3001/documents

### Delete a document (removes the MinIO object too)
### DELETE http://localhost:3001/documents/DOC-2026-04-000099
